{"tid":2379503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"男生去年元旦刑毁滙豐及拒捕罪成 判囚5個半月 官斥行為自私","createTime":"2021-01-25T09:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:58:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"84e1dceb1f760fb61b08e1434d2b2f12d999608b","tid":2379503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:25:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13196&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=030dd713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13196</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第十庭 <br />\n#張志偉裁判官 <br />\n#20200101灣仔 #判刑 #刑事損壞 #拒捕<br />\n<br />\nD2:黎(21)  <br />\n<br />\n(1)刑事損壞 (D2) <br />\n於本年1月1日，在香港灣仔軒尼詩道71號至85號的滙豐銀行分行之外，分別損壞屬分行的木圍板<br />\n<br />\n(3)抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員(D2) <br />\n於本年1月1日，在香港灣仔軒尼詩道71號至85號的滙豐銀行分行之外，抗拒在正當執行職務的警長C<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n<br />\nD1, D3已於2021年1月11日獲判無罪，控罪2及4與D2無關，故案中餘下控罪1及3。<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n已解釋報告內容予被告，報告顯示被告不適合入勞教中心<br />\n<br />\n判刑理由<br />\n<br />\n控罪1<br />\n雖然被告是單獨行事，但其行為：噴上一個「立」字，完成整個「香港獨立的標語」。<br />\n<br />\n整案控罪1判刑以下列4項原因為依據：<br />\n1. 噴的內容<br />\n2. 周遭環境<br />\n3. 可能引發的潛在風險<br />\n4. 造成損害的程度<br />\n<br />\n受害機構需要花費金錢去遮蓋，內容亦會分化香港，有機會造成更多衝擊。雖然沒有造成阻礙，但需要告誡後來者，故以5個月為量刑基礎。<br />\n<br />\n控罪3<br />\n本案中反抗的情況是激烈，並從而令警員受傷，警員應受法律保護，雖然只是抗拒行為，但與侵害人身罪可相比，故以4星期為量刑起點。<br />\n<br />\n判刑：<br />\n控罪1：5個月即時監禁為量刑基準<br />\n控罪3：4星期即時監禁<br />\n<br />\n2項控罪雖時間上相近，但2件事並無關係，不應同期執行，故法庭以其中2個星期分期執行，以顯示整體罪責<br />\n<br />\n總刑期：5個月零2星期❗️<br />\n<br />\n1545 據了解，有可能申請上訴<br />\n<br />\n直播員按：依然諗唔明點解法庭只保護警員，但不保護市民，以同案D3為例，明明受到警暴，但法庭絕口不提。道德高地的裁判官縱容警員使用不合理暴力，以裁判官之名要告誡後來者，卻自身縱容警暴，可笑之說"},{"pid":"51493b7bf0c04b45385560e9e98e548bf0bd0a4a","tid":2379503,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"21歲學生被控去年元旦大遊行期間，塗污灣仔滙豐銀行提款機中心的木圍板，寫上「香港獨立」字眼，又試圖逃離警察追捕。他早前受審後被裁定刑事毁壞及拒捕罪成，今在東區裁判法院被判入獄5個月零2星期，張志偉裁判官斥被告的行為自私，令物主須花錢修補，強調法庭並非限制表達自由，但前題是不能破壞他人財產。<br />\n<br />\n張官判刑時稱，被告的背景報告正面，顯示他有真誠的反省，但他經審訊後被定罪，沒有特殊情況可作減刑因素。張官續指，法庭在判刑時，考慮了被告噴寫的內容、當時的環境、潛在風險及破壞程度；而被告塗寫的字句分化香港社會，令潛在衝突出現。<br />\n<br />\n張官就刑毁罪以5個月監禁為量刑起點；拒捕罪則為2星期。由於兩罪並非接連發生，故刑期分期執行。"},{"pid":"ef0b5968040c103e723d831babc21b770e5d3813","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"其實勞教報告點寫？"},{"pid":"d4a2a234c9da6c52271d28e3c58d9fe05f090af2","tid":2379503,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ded93ea42169d308636eff696ac9a641e5f462c","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef0b5968040c103e723d831babc21b770e5d3813","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"其實勞教報告點寫？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"勞教分分鐘要一年"},{"pid":"f7992be9e420db2c82c91d598692113fa3babad6","tid":2379503,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"去年民陣元旦大遊行，三名男生被指「裝修」滙豐銀行灣仔軒尼詩道分行，經審訊後其中兩人脫罪，餘下一人被裁定刑事毀壞及襲警罪成。裁判官張志偉今日判刑時指出，被告以油漆刑毀，雖無量刑準則，惟噴上「香港獨立」字眼分化社會，造成衝突危機，判囚5個月，至於襲警罪則判囚4星期，其中兩星期刑期分開執行，總共監禁5個月2星期。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情指，黎姓被告因有「漏斗胸」胸壁畸型身體狀況，不適合進入勞教中心。背景報告指出，被告現時修讀金融相關學位課程，原本立志計劃考取金融分析師牌照，現時定罪令機會渺茫。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又指，被告成長雖荊棘滿途，但其品格良好，亦是一位有目標的年輕人。被告與兄長及母親三人互相扶持，母親過往曾有自殺行為，平時被告需照顧患病母親。被告承認行為愚蠢，與其品格不符，已吸取教訓，並反思行為帶來的影響，希望法庭輕判，讓其盡快投入社會。<br />\n<br />\n張官判刑時指，報告內容正面，當中已看到被告為自己的行為作出反省，惟被告過去的良好品格及背景，不可作為減刑因素，案中亦看不到有特殊情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/LEFS4DLZOJC6DNN3SARUDPUOBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FLEFS4DLZOJC6DNN3SARUDPUOBA%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=50351a8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210125%2FLEFS4DLZOJC6DNN3SARUDPUOBA%2F&h=c8aa62da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210125/LEFS4DLZOJC6DNN3SARUDPUOBA/</a>"},{"pid":"7ac889947263b5a838a5422196fa9d6554be1ce7","tid":2379503,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a53b06d671e30376b6a5e23a95461fe289dbd8b","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ded93ea42169d308636eff696ac9a641e5f462c","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef0b5968040c103e723d831babc21b770e5d3813","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"其實勞教報告點寫？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"勞教分分鐘要一年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"多數半年，但我寧願坐好過"},{"pid":"1a306d4eb3f2f9a1827095a27898d5108baeb5a9","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a53b06d671e30376b6a5e23a95461fe289dbd8b","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ded93ea42169d308636eff696ac9a641e5f462c","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef0b5968040c103e723d831babc21b770e5d3813","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:26:36.000Z","msg":"其實勞教報告點寫？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"勞教分分鐘要一年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"多數半年，但我寧願坐好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"係⋯"},{"pid":"c283fbcd959f059d2c2bda886f83a3de1bb11755","tid":2379503,"uid":1327,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"最大愛最無私既人俾呢Ｄ咩都冇付出既人話自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然呢個比喻未必岩<br />\n但我腦中突然想起伽利略發表日心說 地球唔撚係世界中心<br />\n結果被教廷逼死<br />\n而家呢刻香港就係咁邪惡<br />\n奸人當道"},{"pid":"f1637615e0fcbf283a61d1d0110f448695a1f712","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a306d4eb3f2f9a1827095a27898d5108baeb5a9","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a53b06d671e30376b6a5e23a95461fe289dbd8b","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1ded93ea42169d308636eff696ac9a641e5f462c","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"勞教分分鐘要一年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"多數半年，但我寧願坐好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"係⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"但如果身體冇病冇痛就可能勞教"},{"pid":"b21303a84aa6e9d7562ffe35bfef2a25ef20f9cf","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1637615e0fcbf283a61d1d0110f448695a1f712","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a306d4eb3f2f9a1827095a27898d5108baeb5a9","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a53b06d671e30376b6a5e23a95461fe289dbd8b","tid":2379503,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:29:49.000Z","msg":"多數半年，但我寧願坐好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:33:36.000Z","msg":"係⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"但如果身體冇病冇痛就可能勞教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"唔一定嘅 你可以要求唔要勞教"},{"pid":"bc87af00c1015fd2d51327095b6761084b9e2e23","tid":2379503,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82116b5890da6a073fccee484cc12fbcc5ddf86","tid":2379503,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:05:57.000Z","msg":"咁講都幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />噴隻字搞到社會分化同有衝突<br />\n又係無限放大潛在風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a154a93c0d49889c9daa6aa7e59067551aa9a113","tid":2379503,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c283fbcd959f059d2c2bda886f83a3de1bb11755","tid":2379503,"uid":1327,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T09:33:43.000Z","msg":"最大愛最無私既人俾呢Ｄ咩都冇付出既人話自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然呢個比喻未必岩<br />\n但我腦中突然想起伽利略發表日心說 地球唔撚係世界中心<br />\n結果被教廷逼死<br />\n而家呢刻香港就係咁邪惡<br />\n奸人當道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:08:59.000Z","msg":"成個中共本身就係邪惡嘅集合體"},{"pid":"516507c0edf8adb865cf5ee78f28e169ca8b02bf","tid":2379503,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2865b385b52dc0c9429d80ed011a3b2f277c19bd","tid":2379503,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ded93ea42169d308636eff696ac9a641e5f462c","tid":2379503,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef0b5968040c103e723d831babc21b770e5d3813","tid":2379503,"uid":23148